Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打从心里大叫一句\N好想快点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信总有一天\N一定能相遇相知永结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望你能追着我的背影而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我孤单一人只为等候你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落英缤纷的春日午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将祈祷转为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你不会忘记最重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快啊\N下礼拜就要举行婚礼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们刚去给惣一郎扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,五代\N响子就拜托你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始可能会让她吃苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始过得勤俭节约一点\N也比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎也可以安心长眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#96只要这份爱还在!\N永远的一刻馆!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N就这样继续住在管理员室?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊\N搬家需要花一笔很大的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且音无家的爸爸\N也已经答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以暂时会住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是精打细算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费是最大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么东西要烧的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有新婚的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是第二次结婚了\N也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以丢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,这个也麻烦你烧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你第一次结婚\N拍的婚纱照吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,不可以啦\N怎么可以随便翻别人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要看,我也要看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有新娘子的感觉耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你看你看\N管理员的婚纱照很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦\N没有必要强迫他看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次看到\N惣一郎的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是个很温柔的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有必要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不能把这些东西\N放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是些结婚照而已\N没有什么好在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道一切事情\N才决定结婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么会去在意这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子的心情\N应该也早就整理好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惣一郎的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就会拿去还给音无家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好像很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,我并没有舍不得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N我应该早点还给他们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必勉强还给他们也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要做个了断,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跟管理员吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就吵架\N以后日子会很难过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有吵架啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊\N那我去看“福星小子”的录影带好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后的日子…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再来一碗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我得出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我会去一趟音无家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归还遗物的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟惣一郎说一声才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来这里做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我很羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使将遗物归还音无家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想响子也绝对\N不可能忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这不是忘不忘记的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早已经成为\N响子心中的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我会继续努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到响子的时候\N她心中就已经有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上的就是这样的响子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要连你一起,把响子娶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我能遇到这个人\N你一定会为我感到高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你怎么来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要问你呢,幼稚园呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我趁午休时间偷溜出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的遗物\N等一下我要把它拿去还给爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你听我说\N那个真的没必要勉强归还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够遇见你,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,爷爷,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是郁子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点都认不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公,快来\N音无家的亲家公来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好久不见了\N你变得好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母,不要糗我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是贤太郎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,你一点都没变耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,一直都长不高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法啊\N都是妈妈的遗传
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子婶婶打扮好了没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那五代哥哥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张得半死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好帅的新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来得真早\N结婚典礼还没开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向公司报外出溜出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也很仰慕管理员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很羡慕我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子婶婶打扮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去看看,快去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是住在横须贺的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候你还只有这么小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我们都不担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公,你也说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出来是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷,快来啊,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几年来\N真的很感谢你的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我等这一天等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管去找你的幸福吧\N连以前的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为了今天\N才来到这个世上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,脸上的妆会花掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(本日已被包下店长)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,椅子不够耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,欢迎新郎新娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜,恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜,恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-部长\N-老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都来啦\N谢谢你们,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么大家来干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,啤酒啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上铺张报纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,你来得正好\N现在才要开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N因为我去了一趟医院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生病了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,不要害羞了\N快点进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子真的好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是双胞胎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话\N我才要恭喜你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看起来很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,不要这样啦\N太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么好丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么值得庆贺的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,你也来跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请新郎倌五代\N为大家致辞答谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很感谢各位来参加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在终于可以\N当一名称职的褓父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前发生过许多不如意的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,从学生时代开始\N当我痛苦难过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏现在在场的各位亲友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严厉的指责或是鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在仍是个靠不住的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后说不定\N还会给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟这里的响子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟响子两人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起努力生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢各位\N-谢谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好舒服的风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好可以醒醒酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这身和服好不习惯\N腰酸背痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是在饭店订了房间吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜月旅行下午才出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们想住在一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,我们回去慢慢喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然敲定了,就快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家,回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我回来了\N-我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样,日子一天天过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里住习惯了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就适应这里的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我老公陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧姓七尾小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定居名古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻和睦,生活美满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰瞬,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生了一对双胞胎女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三胎也指日可待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去联谊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以认识帅哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神伊吹,正在念女子大学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是干嘛\N你已经有认识帅哥了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神的心\N好像还留在高中时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还无法忘记老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太专情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你嫁给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,你不是有太太了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经分居好几年\N最近终于正式离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六本木朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在住在茶茶丸的二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着,樱花的季节又到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,这是老板叫我带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员是今天出院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,差不多就要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他们两人\N今后有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们明明说\N生了小孩之后就要搬离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是继续住下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,这样很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,让我看看小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸红通通的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟爸爸一样健康
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个女孩吧,名字决定了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取作春天的香味,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,春香,真是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香,我们回到家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈\N第一次见面的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在五号房\N我叫五代裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面,从今天起\N我是这栋公寓的管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫音无响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(相聚一刻全剧终)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该知道这不是擦身而过的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻也是…woo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢一个人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.44,0:24:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.25,0:24:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.05,0:24:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这烛火依偎着的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.39,0:24:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝视着你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.20,0:24:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着将至今的谎言吹熄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.04,0:25:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.74,0:25:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.25,0:25:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我行不通…woo

